text: The product shall record different meeting types.
The product shall be able to send meeting notifications via different kinds of end-user specified methods.
The product shall have an intuitive user interface.
IzognMovies shall meet the licensing requirements set forth by the appropriate organizations in order to stream African movies.

The product must work with most database management systems (DBMS) on the market  whether the DBMS is colocated with the product on the same machine or is located on a different machine on the computer network.
The product will be available for licensing as a one-server  two-five servers  or five-or-more servers license.
The product shall respond fast to keep up-to-date data in the display.
The product shall be able to support multiple remote users
The product shall allow for intuitive searching of available conference rooms.
The product shall be intuitive and self-explanatory.  Nine out ten users shall be able to successfully complete a game with no training.
